nodes.text: Aurren Panteer was a Human male who served as Lord of House Panteer during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. He was the nephew of the Queen Silara Panteer. Around 3643 BBY, he dispatched an elite detachment of the Queensguard to accompany the Sith with the intention of arresting Bouris Ulgo.
